STBLKeyStringList.Text: Snazzy Squiggle
A cloudy frame and fun, pastel sheets set the stage for your most colorful and happy dreams.
Poppy Pocket Bed
Make this artistically arched bookcase the centerpiece of your personal haven! Fill it with your favorite Social Bunny book recs and collections of memorabilia.
Retro Reader Bookcase
You and your friends decide to use the archaic practice of etching your messages in ink. Pin them here so they're easy to see! Heart and thumb stickers not included.
Squiggly Squaggly Communication Board

Not enough space for a computer or desktop setup? This adorable portable tablet with a matching mouse and keyboard is sure to liven up your space. With tons of color options, get your work done in style wherever you go.
The Aesthetically Portable Tablet
A staple in the Aesthetic series, this desk comes in multiple swatches to fit all your pastel needs. With its two-tiered design, keep your study organized or pile it with clutter!
The Aesthetic Tiered Desk
Inspired by the iconic pool noodle, these squiggly candles will light up any space. Just...don't put it in a pool.
The Noodle Candle
Light up your space with a little amber glow, maybe mull over the secrets locked in such a rock.
Lamp Finds a Way
Have you ever seen a puddle on the ground and thought, "Wow, I wish I could hang this on the wall." Well, now you can! And better yet, there's two. Enjoy!
Double Puddle Wall Mirror
With plenty of pastel swatches to choose from, your walls will never look cuter with these framed prints from the Aesthetic series.
The Aesthetic Print Set
At first glance, you might think you're stepping on a huge cookie. But don't worry! This rug is soft and won't crumble.
Cute Cookie Rug
All the season's most popular patterns in one place! Enjoy making your berry bedroom, cow print cozy space, or groovy roost a place all your own.
Choose Your Aesthetic Rug

This resin vase and felted flower are the only remnant of a craft you just had to make, of a hobby you just had to have, and all the materials boxed away in that one closet of all the other things you just had to try. There's no sense throwing it all out as you'll probably want to do it again in a year or two anyway. Instead you enjoy its presence, along with everything else that makes up the aesthetic you'll probably be done with in a couple months.
Fondly Felted Floral Creation
No matter your mood or style, you'll always look cute in this Luv Heart mirror. With a few hooks for your must-have items, you'll always be ready to go.
Luv Heart Wall Mirror

Who said shelves couldn't be fun? Make your walls pop with this geometric wall shelf from the Aesthetic series! Display your knick knacks to your heart's content with its perfectly measured slots to brighten up any room.
The Aesthetic Wall Shelf

This cute office chair is both sweet and functional. Made with high quality materials and a stylish design, this fun chair will make you look at the world in a whole new way. So go ahead – do what you love to do.
Luv 2 Work Office Chair
This chair was designed to give you the coziest place to read, binge your favorite shows, or scroll too much on Social Bunny and run out of things to look at. Great for just refreshing the page, too.
Hug Me A Lot Chair by Cozy Corner Creations
This simple little love seat is just so aesthetically satisfying. Sleek and simple, but soft and round, it's cozy in all the right places!
Smoothly Satisfying Sofa by Cozy Corner Creations

If, given the two options of Bouba or Kiki, most Sims would likely refer to this table as Bouba. This is a scientifically proven fact. I mean, look at it. Semiotically speaking, its name is obviously Bouba. Kiki would require more sharp edges, right? Someone back me up here!
Bouba (Not Kiki) Table

Don't let your dreams be dreams! This end table is for that type of room that's only limited by your imagination and lets your mind go anywhere. A room where you can experience all those imaginary adventures. Those adventures where you might even meet your evil self from another timeline. Adventures that might help you to predict the future! Is it actually a table though? Or could it also be something entirely different? The Imaginariums End Table knows no limits and there's only one way for you to find out!
Imaginariums End Table

The Imaginariums Hallway Table redefines the rules of space and time. "Out in the universe, time is not a straight line! It's a curve!", its creator once said. And so it came to pass that this time-less and innovative piece of furniture, breaking with the conventions of precisely angled table legs, was created.
Imaginariums Hallway Table
This is the perfect trash can to blend in with your room. It has the cutest designs and comes with its very own inactive but very clicky foot pedal for fidgety feet!
Gimme A Click Trash Can
Sweet Suite
Berry Bundle
Still Waters Run Deep
